				say "     You can't help but be impressed with the workmanship of hir platinum emerald laden nipple chain and ruby dragon's eye necklace as Arlene's prodigious J-cup mounds, swollen with hir untold bounty strains against them delectable with hir every breath. Shimmer with a rich sheen of natural lubricant, hir bountifully engorged with hir sumptuous mother's milk and puffy nips constantly drip with a heavenly sheen of pearly cream. Profoundly priceless, an endless conga line of your followers bearing large golden urns mill about the temple grounds while they wait their chance both to fill them and to pay homage to your chosen. The buxom humans worshipfully crowd about hir perky mammoth tits as they knead and massage your priestesses plush groaning orb with loving alacrity. Their supple fingers shamelessly sink into hir productive fatty while they coax thick streams of cream from hir puffy ducts. Some of your more adventurous followers still pause in their task to sup directly from Arlene's pieced pink nips, or gently lap at any errant that dare defile your gravid mate's tender body.";
				if Loyalty of Arlene is 2:
					say "     Lost in hir own personal paradise, your gluttonous breeder pays them any mind or even seems all that aware of their presence, as hir paws roam the awe inspiring curves of hir ponderous tumby. Far larger than shi is, the horny herm can barely even wrap hir portly arm around the sweltering mass of spawn laden bump as it decadently lazes over hir beastly digitigrade leg like a quivering mountain of fertile excess. Though that doesn't stop the titanic broodmare from gleefully groping vast pawfulls of lube and oil slicked skin as if to bask in hir heavenly proportions. Hir alabaster tumby is almost completely covered in thick sensual ruby red stretches that seem to deepen by the second as hir body struggles to keep pace with not just rapid growth of your spawn, but Arlene's own ravenous appetite. As the glowing grey love handles swaddling hir heaving tum alone could easily swallow a man whole in their plush toasty folds, while hir sensitive robust outie has blossomed to truly ostentatious proportions is not a rather catching eye center piece to hir splendor, but has become a potent symbol of hir boundless affinity for gravidity."; 
					say "     Spurred on by hir example and the hopes that some of Arlene's blessing may rub off on them, your cultist now openly vie for the chance to lay hands upon hir fecund majesty or offer their prayers for salvation to your slumbering brood. Though the most committed breeders are allowed the honor of pampering hir beautiful bump as such, a renewed wave of baby fever is has swept the cult. The rest content themselves with feeding the priestess's boundless appetite or pampering pleasing plump body, as even in hir opulent state, the craving of exotic fare and delicious drink imposed upon hir by your innumerable eggs are more than a little taxing. To their credit, your eager follower and chosen Seradovah servants perform their tasks admirably despite Arlene's voracious appetite as teams of dutiful feeders clamber about hir nest as they try to tempt the insatiable herm with some fine dish or precious juices."; 
					say "    All of which only serves to fuel hir splendid growth as hir upper arms are swaddled in untold inches of supple tallow leading down to a cute taper near hir wrists.  Nevertheless, hir Rubenesque arms are well at home resting against hir pudgy frame, or being pampered by your doting followers as they lovingly massaged the folds decorating hir plush body. Still, they serve a comfortable pillow for your brood as they nurse or Arlene's handmaidens during the rare moments shi sleeps. Despite profoundly hir portly nature, Arlene's connection to the goddess, Kia Monah, and by extension you has never been greater, nor have hir communion been more popular as any silly pretense of decorum or scripture has been thrown to the wayside in favor of raw carnal pleasure and gluttonous satisfaction. Under your priestesses tutelage, alongside the constant influx of the sea nanite laced bounty, your cultists have fully surrendered to their bodies desire for food and sex while they parade their plush gravid bellies, and heaving milky breasts before you in the hopes they might earn your approval. In time, they will all become little more than happy, bubbly incubators swaddled in succulent adipose with no thought beyond their next meal, fling, or servicing your flight's needs.";
				else if Loyalty of Arlene is 1:
					say "     Utterly enthralled by the attention paid to hir own brood flush body, shi lovingly encourages your follower's playful antics as the doting humans gleefully pamper hir toasty middle. Even eager to please, the affectionate mortals are more than happy to oblige hir as they diligently caress and massage the glowing folds of hir mountainous tum ringed by glistening handles. Almost as large shi is, your puny by comparison cultists are dwarfed by the doughy swell of alabaster tummy. Even at half hir body's capacity, the ponderous mass of supple midriff easily obscures much of hir well-padded quad medicine ball size cum tanks and juicy cock slit are visible behind the voluptuous blanket of hand swallowing adipose. Almost drunk with motherly hormones and the blissful presence of your eggs putting pressure on the right places, hir puffy dick slit leaks a light stream of salty pre, while the crimson tip of hir foot long prehensile tool occasionally slips free of its lovely housing. "; 
					say "     Arlene's thick meaty broodmare-esque waist and digitigrade legs capped by hir power draconic paws and five ivory toe talons still retain some of their shapely qualities, though it's impossible to deny the supple beauty of lush material padding coating hir leg in layer of jiggly tallow. Meanwhile, hir plush outie ringed with dense spire of ruby stretch mark too has grown all the more prominent and sensitive a the merest brush of your followers fingers in enough to evoke a cute little pant from the lustful demi-dragon. Totally devoted to their mistress's growth, scores zealous of worshipers fawn over the jiggly home of your titanic spawn as they slather hir tigerstrip kissed womb in a fresh sheen of sweet smelling oils. While other dutifully followers accompanied by teams of handpicked Seradovah feeders, their arms packed with plates of succulent treats alongside massive crystal of exotic juices mill about hir chambers as tirelessly work to satisfy both your mate's craving and your spawn's ravenous appetites."; 
					WaitLineBreak;
					say "     Not that shi needs much encouragement, as Arlene's rising obsession with hir preferred state along with all the power and wealth it brings hir is more than apparent in ways shi proudly gropes hir plush eggy middle with hir chubby paws. Hir draconic eyes alight with manic glee as shi basks in the tender softness protectively swaddling hir bulky body and the heady weight of your spawn as they mold hir into the perfect vessel. Occasionally though, the greedy half-half will scoops vast pawfull of coins and precious gems from hir nest with hir tendrils then drizzles them over fecund curves delighting at the pleasant click of hir hoard cascading over over hir while the rich hues of hir horde reflect in the ambient torch light as they plink off fecund middle. Another time, you might have chastised members of your flock for such displays, yet the crown jewel of your cult's grandeur has earned the right to wallow in riches shi has brought in as the power and connection to you and the goddess only deepening with hir girth and gravidity.";
