			-- "Have some hyper preg sex?":
				say "     You idly rub your powerful draconic paws over the lush swell of your brood-laden middle in raw delight at the sensual smoothness of your taut oily scales gliding across your pads as you absentmindedly pamper the growing outlines of your spawn slumbering. While you eye up the plush ponderous tumby of your equally eggy priestess, and decide to have a little [']mommy time['] with the buxom herm. After all, you both deserve a chance to blow off some steam in your current state, you muse, as the wondrous cocktail of maternal hormones bubbling through your [bodydesc of Player] core has left you more than a little on edge lately. A sentiment that seems to be shared by Arlene, as your sharp draconic senses can easily smell the exotic scent of hir hybrid arousal coiling through the room as the increasingly heavy set breeder labors under the lush weight of your titanic spawn. The poor herm is barely able to stand, much less waddle in hir current state as hir overstretched tummy dominates every aspect of hir life as your goliath clutch nearly dwarfs your favored plaything. Though from the proud little glint in hir eyes as shi lovingly traces a single pointer claw along the vibrant crimson spiderweb of tiger stripes gracing hir heaving bump, you know shi wouldn't have it any other way.";
				say "     'Da, admiring yar handy work, me dragon?' shi hums, draping hir arms over the lush groaning curves of her gorgeous G-cups. Swollen with purpose and rich cream, hir decadent mounds maintain a certain shapely quality that few mothers hir size could match, as they comfortably wobble atop hir heavenly tum with hir every laborious breath. Rumbling contentedly, you tell hir that it's hard not to, besides, the new look suits hir. 'Yar, ye be too kind to dis [']ere old sea dog, me heart,' shi purrs, as hir webbed palms drift along the tender swell of hir rack in open admiration. 'Nots dat I'z don'ts be appreciating da attention, evens if yer wee ones can be a right ravenous bunch,' she titters, giving hir perky nips an affectionate squeeze. 'Still, ta gifts dem un her worshipfulness be sharing with me be more den worth da hassle,' shi preens, watching twin glittering beads of pearly perfection seep between the gaps in hir fingers. Chuffing in reply, you express more than a touch of satisfaction in knowing that their blessings are being put to good use. 'Indeed day are me heart, course, I'z see I'z not ta only one what's enjoying ta lady's gifts,' Arlene simpers, eyeing up your own fecund middles.";
				WaitLineBreak;
				say "     Naturally, you preen, as you advance upon hir with a proud predatory sashay, reveling in the subtle bounce of your assets and gentle click of your talons upon the floor. Though boons such as yours deserve to be shared with a like-minded soul, wouldn't shi agree? You tease, pressing your verdant bump against hirs, exalting in the dissonant kiss of your glossy scales gliding along hir coarse well-lubed skin. 'Ay me lovely, I'z couldn't uv asked for a better mate, or partner,' your priestess coos, cheekily wrapping hir mitts about the lush swell of your gleaming middle. Gnarring happily at hir tender touch and light kiss of hir claws gracing your scales, you proffer that perhaps the two of you should take a moment to enjoy the spoils of your continued alliance and, you pause, working your dominant forepaws about hir waist, groping a supple pawful of hir shapely selachian ass, your growing bounty. 'Da ya took da words right out [']O me mouth boyo,' Arlene chuckles, motioning to an unoccupied stretch of the plush furry carpeting gracing hir humble quarters with a theatrical flick of hir finned tail.";
				say "     Smirking at hir suggestion, you strut over to the convenient patch of open space and leisurely drape yourself across the cushy hides with a grateful sigh at the satin caress of the wondrous fur gracing your paws, and oh-so-sensitive scales as you roll onto your back. Mh, feels good to get off your feet, you chuckle, beckoning your doting priestess over with a come hither wave of your augmented tail. 'Da, un da view be something to admire too, me sultry sea devil. Why I'z dares ta reckon thar be no finer sight in da neath den yar abyssal beauty, me dragon,' the eager shark herm purrs, selachian eyes drifting along the opalescent curves of your eggy core. Almost blushing at hir praise, your draconic mind can't help but agree, as your many golden glowing orbs waltz along the hills of your supple scalie middles. The growing swell of your assets as you take in the heavenly sight of your brood laden body. Oh-so-ripe and devilishly powerful, the spectacle of your imposing fertile frame rarely fails to bring a toothy smile to your scaley lips. You muse, drinking in the beatific radiance of your molten gaze refracting off the regal lamina lining your draconic limbs.";
				WaitLineBreak;
				say "     The sense of raw bestial might and unearthly potential builds in your taut not-so-little bumps by the second as your slumbering spawn grow all the larger. Soon, some proud facet of your cold-blooded maternal mind crows as you playfully paw at your lush feral core, you'll be able to hold these wondrous wyrms in your arm and share with them all gifts the goddess has bestowed upon you. 'Course,' Arlene coos, wrapping hir hand beneath the plush curves of hir monumental tummy as shi makes a show of hefting hir taut middle out of the way of hir cute dick slit as shi nestles hir profoundly gravid body behind you. 'I'z like ta think I'z be coming a close second tea ye,' shi crows, carefully lower hir plush baby bump atop yours as shi tucks hir athletic hips between your splayed draconic legs. Perhaps, you tease, wrapping your forepaws about hir lush figure, and gently grazing your scything reflective talons along the resplendent swell of hir rosy tiger-striped midriff, relishing the supple weight of Arlene's brood pressing down upon you. Shi certainly shows potential, who knows, in time shi might even give your regal form a run for its money.";
