					say "      Hir twin spires thumb delectable at each sensual pass of your tendrils and aquatic walls pamper hir glossy spires in their vivacious embrace as you fix hir with a smoldering look as you hum. Go on pet, cum, while [if intelligence of Galaxite is 2]your feelers reverently massage the spasming borders of hir G-spots and compact cum tanks[else]you arc your spaded tail about the elated contours of hir g-spots[end if] in a sordid ballet of hybrid ecstasy. Your plaything can only whimper in reply as the Seradovah supporting hir coils their glittering tails about hir shaky legs for support as if to urge hir on. Leaning into their embrace, your plaything fervently bucks hir hips with the last waning ounces of hir strength[if intelligence of Galaxite is 2] while your tendrils squirm about your dripping passaging in a decadent spiral of rollicking sensation[end if] as shi cums with a relieved sigh. Hir ripe cum veins bulge ever-so-slightly with the toasty weight of hir load roiling about hir spires as shi loose a torrent of selachin seed upon your slutty folds.";
					WaitLineBreak;
					say "     Rumbing with bestial draconic satisfaction at the heavenly warmth seeping your core, you can feel your hungring walls cinch about about hir spent spires in a decadent dandle as your ravenous body seems to drink in hir lovely offering. Your raw cunny muscles soon spasm like an overloaded switch board as you cum once more with a contented rumble as your palms drift to ";
					if Player is impreg_now:
						say "the tender curves of your well-loved middle as the tumultuous echoes of static delight course across your scales. You can't help but urge your brood to drink in your priestess's blessed load while lovingly pampering their slumbering form with paws, relishing the thought that one day soon you'll be holding your precious spawn in your arms. And together share in the wondrous destiny that a waits you both in day to come.";
					else if Player is impreg_able:
						say "the yearning curves of your [bodydesc of Player] respective tum, rollicking at vibrant tendrils of coldblooded satisfaction simmering though your muff as you thoughtlessly whisper a prayer to the goddess urging her to let this load stick. As your body craves the priceless euphoric bliss only your brood can bring you, you muse while the heavenly memory of your maternal splendor fills your mind's eye. You can't help but purr at the thought of feeling your body ripen once more with divine life, and all the blissful changes your preferred state brings. As intoxicating images of your growing curves perched atop vast oceans of treasure and army of thralls attending your and your chosen's every need briefly wash over you.";
					say "     Your now spent priestess, sways ever-so-slightly on hir shuddering legs, barely even able to support hir burgeoning body as shi eases hirself into the waiting embrace of the Seradovah's coils with a contented sigh. 'Yarg feelz like I'z about ta pop,' shi hums, proudly pawing at hir heaving tum as the flush rosy hem of hir bloated belly spills out across hir while your mate's supple tools soften within your muff's aquatic embrace. Chuffing happily at the sight, you can't help but enjoy the spectacle of hir groaning curves and the parting caress of hir cocks as they leisurely glide along your silky passage and supple button as you playfully tell how hir how adorable shi looks like this. 'Daw, ya be too kind to dis [']ere old sea sow. Doe,' Arlene purrs, leaning into your gaze, 'I'z must admit dis I'z could be getting used to dis me heart,' while shi lovingly drapes hir arms over the deepening folds of hir turgid tum. 'Specially when I'z got des boyos to take care of me,' shi adds, bobbing hir head towards the Seradovah supporting hir lush form.";
					WaitLineBreak;
					say "     Of course, you chuff in agreement as you carefully withdraw your [if intelligence of Galaxite is 2]tentacular[else]ovi[end if] tail with a fanciful flourish, after all hir new curves and servants suit hir. 'Yar-har, all say me dragon, this accord of our be working out right fine, un doe I'z never thought meself cut fir do clothe, service to her ladyship be a might bit more [']fulfilling['] den me days prowling da deep blue.' Arlene preens, reclining out upon the Seradovah's ponderous coils as if to bask in hir glorious condition. 'Why, jus tink-[']N [']bout all da petty plots un schemes me un da [one of]ladz[or]boyz[or]grotz[at random] would weave all ta nick a few bobble er trinket when we'z couldz [']O been working fir her ladyship be boggling da mind,' shi rumbles, wistfully. Nodding, you express a similar sentiment as your meager struggles in the city and your old life seem like such a puny compared to the destiny that awaits you now. 'Aya me dragon, *yawn* un dare be no other soul I'd wish ta share dat with.' Arlene hums sleepily, sinking into your thralls coils as shi slowly drifts off to sleep in the naga's protective glossy coils. In no mood to disturb hir, or your spawn's peaceful slumber, you quietly paw over to hir bed, gather a few blankets and drape the over hir bountiful from before departing.";
				NPCSexAftermath Player receives "PussyFuck" from Arlene;
				NPCSexAftermath Arlene receives "PussyDildoFuck" from Player;
