					increase Libido of Arlene by 3;
				if Libido of Arlene is 0:
					now Libido of Arlene is 1;
				if Cock Count of Player >= 1:
					NPCSexAftermath Player receives "Stroking" from Arlene;
				Move Player to Dragon's Causeway;
	else:
		say "     [italic type]Author's Note[roman type]: Arlene's scenes are not compatable with non-pureblooded Dragon Breeder.";

