under sea is a situation.
ResolveFunction of under sea is "[ResolveEvent under_da_sea]".
Sarea of under sea is "Nowhere".

to say ResolveEvent under_da_sea:
	say "    Prowling along the soft pearly white and gold sands gracing this desolate, yet unerringly placid section of this alleged former pirate enclave, you can find neither scale nor fin of the Seradovah said to be patrolling this place. Then again, the rough surf battering this modest islet alongside the countless caverns lining the area's craggy interior offer quite a great deal of cover, even for beings as large and intimidating as the hunky nagas. You muse, passing by the various mouths of some of the more sizable cave entrances, worn by the constant ebb and flow of the tides and pitted with barnacle holes, both old and new. The local slate has taken on an almost lunar quality as strange channels accompanied by odd bellies in the rock running across the stone at chaotic angles that stretch deep into the gloomy briny depth. Flaring your chromatophores for effect, you bathe the area in a soft bone white as you peer all the further into the umbral pall, only to find this rocky tube ends in a rubble strewn puddle no larger than a kiddy pool full of brackish salt water laden with detritus and crushed sea shells.";
	say "     Shaking your proud scalie visage in mild irritation, you head back to the churning surf and momentarily consider submerging yourself in the waves once more to ping the Seradovah with your budding eldritch sonar, but swiftly abandon the idea. You have no interest in peering at the horrid wound festering in their breast again any time soon, or at least until you figure out some why to avoid being drawn in by it. Though it galls you to no end to be forced to wait upon your lessers thusly, you decide it best to simply stay near the water's edge. Besides, you ruminate, the trip here was not exactly the easiest, so why not take a few minutes to sit back and rest till the lowly puppet things reveal themselves. You muse, selecting a mostly clean patch of sand some distance from the crashing waves then gently lower yourself onto your back and tuck your arms behind your head as bask in the [if daytimer is day]warm rays of the sun as they play across your velvety scales[else if daytimer is night]brilliant starlight as the muted glow of the vibrant nightsky shimmers along your silky lamina[end if] while you wait.";
	WaitLineBreak;
	say "     [italic type]An indeterminate amount of time passes[roman type], and beyond the pleasant of hymns of the wave curling around you, or the faint songs of seabirds nesting in hidden rocky lees dotting the inner island delighting your ears, very little has happened since you first laid down. Grumbling in aggravation, you prop your upper half up to stare balefully at the coiling off-green waters and swirling alabaster white caps inching ever closer to you as the tide steadily rises. Though as your enhanced vision combs though at the assort flotsam and jetsam milling through the waves, you spy an odd ripple of lustrous gold and gossamer emerald fluttering through the surf. At first glance, you give it little notice, merely assuming the minor anomaly to be nothing more than brightly colored plastic, or perhaps a buoy shorn free of its mooring by the eldritch storm you helped herald in. Yet, as it slithers along the boundaries of the Quiet Sandbar, your augmented senses quickly spot a purposeful pattern in its movement as a spined sail soon peeks out of the frothing waters as it barrels towards you.";
	say "     Though momentary flickers of alarm ripple through your mind, the instant passes quicker than it came as the cold numbing balm of recognition washes over you as you whisper Seradovah under your breath as its statuesque hybrid's crocodilian muzzle breaches the surface and a pair of reflective yet oddly dull slitted eyes lock onto you while it slithers onto shore. Took them long enough, you huff, as you ready a well-deserved tirade for the indolent cur, then recall these soulless automatons have no hope of comprehending your ire, so any attempts at unbraiding one would be foolish waste of your time. You grumble with an aggravated shake of your head as pull yourself to your full height and watch as it slinks on to shore. Though for all its tardiness, you can't say that you aren't enjoying the light spectacle of the ribbons of sea water cascading down their burly shoulders and tough rippling pecs as the impressive demi-leviathan glides along the crisp blues waters. Or the lovely glint of its scales as the dense ripcord muscles lining its lengthy tail and shapely ass shimmer in available light as it silently slithers upon the pearly dunes to bow before, intoning, 'Nah se sturm slayrak Vaysun da Kai Monah,' pounding its bony fists into the sand, sending a brief rumble through the ground.";
	Project Figure of Seradodovah_soft_icon;
	WaitLineBreak;
	say "     Bidding it to rise, though you doubt it understands you much less has any true concept of the world around it beyond whatever its order were, you nevertheless watch as it jerks itself into an ophidian standing position rumbling. 'Fellow... temple... below,' in a dry mechanical mantra as it glides past you towards one of the smaller caverns nestled along the borders of the Quiet Sandbar. Never once though does it stop to look back to see if you're heeding its words, nor does it cease its senseless prattle as it edges its massive frame through the stony aperture. Rolling your many eyes, you begrudgingly hurry after it before the creature fully dips out of sight, propelled by your powerful lower half, you catch up to it in seconds and march in lockstep behind the enthralled scalie. Together you trudge through the gloomy twisting paths while the comforting sound of the ocean waves and ambient light peter away each second till only your draconic radiance and the monotone chant of the Seradovah are left to keep you company.";
	say "     Deeper in, the area grows all the colder as the rocky floor steadily gives way to silt-rich muck that clings to your webbed paws and the sickeningly sweet scents of ancient aquatic decay laced with earthy tangs whose origins you can't quite place with each step you take. Which only serves to fuel your growing ire, as the minutes drag on, you briefly asking your [']guide['] how much longer this will take, yet you doubt the mindbroken creature knows, or even has the ability to answer you even if it did. You ruminate, watching the hulking thrall pause at the edges of a vast impossibly still pond appearing out of the shadows. Chirping to itself in some broken tongue, the creature rears back and dives head first into the stagnant filth-laden liquid. You can feel tendrils of revulsion clawing at the back of your mind at the notion of defiling your draconic beauty by submerging yourself in such rot, yet you quickly bite back against the rising tide of bile surging in your breast and flare your chromatophores all the brighter then dive in after them.";
	WaitLineBreak;
	say "     All the while you try to suppress your resplendent body's natural instinct to invoke the power for your eldritch eyes as you swim down through the narrow passageway as the fetid soup of silt and decay sullies your senses like a blighted shroud. Blessedly, the water soon begins to brighten to a brilliant and clear blue as the caverns widen enough that even a Sea Tyrant could easily slip through as you descend, guided by the low hum of the Seradovah. Offhandedly though, your tendrils sense a mild change in the water as the slight almost imperceptible tug of a faint current washes over them as you glide through the passageway. Unbothered you continue on through the various switchbacks and sudden drops till the craggy disjointed heteromorphic rock gives way to a smooth section of gleaming slate formed into a partial u-bend. Here your companion at last ceases its muted mantra, and bolts straight up towards a low flicker of white synthetic light. With nowhere to go but up, you surge after them and burst free of the water's embrace with a mighty flap of your wings and you find yourself standing in the middle of vast underground moon pool illuminated by small cylindrical electric ";
	if "Touched by Madness" is listed in feats of Player:
		say "torches.";
	else:
		say "lanterns.";
	say "     Though you can't say that you're an expert in such things, to your layman's eye the area appears to have been recently excavated as the rough slate walls are covered in fresh claw marks alongside fragments of waste rock. Casting your abyssal gaze about the area, you watch as the Seradovah slithers northwards towards a rent in the bedraggled rock and soon vanishes from your abyssal sight. Shrugging, you prowl on after them without sparing the Moon Pool a second glance, and as you slip through the unfinished opening in the earth you are greeted by the grinning salachine face of the bawdy pirate shark captain flanked on either side by almost a score of nude caucasian women whose ages range from their mid twenties to late thirties with hair colors varying from platinum blonde to fiery ginger. Molded by the harshness of the nanite outbreak, their bodies are toned and athletic yet still retain a modest degree of their feminine curves as their hourglass waists and trim swimmers thighs impart a classical beauty to their unaltered bodies.";
	WaitLineBreak;
	Project Figure of Priestess_clothed_icon;
	say "     Going by the awestruck looks on their comely faces and gentle blush of their tight freshly-shaved cunts illuminated by your draconic splendor as you walk in, they were not only expecting you, but overjoyed by your arrival. Supple D-cups and dainty B-cups decorate their charming cores, by no means impressive with current state of the sex-crazed and ofttimes hyper inhabitants, the little humans wear them well enough, you muse watching the puff out their chests as your molten gaze washes over them. The captain hirself though seems to have picked up a modicum of [']clothing['] too as thin string bikini top now coddles hir impressive E-cups along with a primal necklace composed of woven hide laced with polished stone, shark's teeth, and lesser sea dragon fangs. Perhaps sensing your eyes drift over to hir, the buxom corsair clears hir throat and steps forward yelling, 'Alright ya sea nymphs look lively now, for ya stand before our most worshipful lady's champion and herald of our salvation, the vaysun da Kai Monah! The scourge of worlds, Nursemaid to dragons, and the most holy archangel of domination, submission, and servitude!'";
	say "     The assembled humans quickly press their mitts to their breasts and link their fingers to form the same draconic symbol that your spawn displayed as they drop to their knees, murmuring in awe of your abyssal glow and titanic frame. 'Goddess they're so beautiful,' one hums. 'Such regal scales,' another gushes. 'By Tiamat I can't believe they're here,' a third mews. 'Fuck I want them inside me,' a forth wimpers as they eagerly prostrate themselves before you. Chuffing at their proper display of deference to your majesty, you take a quick moment to look around the area and, much to your dismay, this alleged temple is little more than a hole bored into the ground. True, you ruminate, it's somewhat unreasonable to expect a handful of apes and Seradovah to build you a chapel worthy of your imperial presence so soon, even if they had sea tyrants to aid them. Perhaps in time, improvement can be made, still they did an admirable for lesser beings as they seem to have already started expanding your domain outwards from this central area.";
	WaitLinebreak;
	say "     You think to yourself as the captain struts besides you, flashing you a quick but knowing look as shi makes a poor attempt at a bottomless curtsy saying, 'Now I'z knows what yar thinking me most regal and benevolent dragon, these puny hall taint much to look at. Un da flock be mighty small tat da moment, but dar hearts be in it and with uz around to help [']bolster da ranks['],' shi chuckles, webbed mitts shamelessly drifting to hir tight cream tum as shi playfully traces hir talons along hir cute little belly button. 'We'z be able to pretty this place up right [']N proper like, of course,' shi adds, spinning on the balls of paws and motions to your supplicants. 'The girls could use a might pinch [']O guidance in how our great and terrible mistress wishes to run this place. Now taint that right me lovelies?' the captain asks, in a pleasant trill as shi motions for the humans to lift their heads with a commanding wave of hir tail. 'Yes Lady Arlene!' the humans rumble in unison as they fix you with a doting expectant stare.";
	LineBreak;
	say " [bold type]Author's note: your decision here will have drastic effects on your cult, the available sex scenes, and potentially your Dragon Breeder body. As these effects are permanent would you like some minor spoilers, or go in blind?[roman type]";
	LineBreak;
	let Spoiler_and_stuff_Choices be a list of text;
	add "Spoil me Dovah daddy!" to Spoiler_and_stuff_Choices; 
	add "No thanks." to Spoiler_and_stuff_Choices;	
	let Spoiler_and_stuff_Choice be what the player chooses from Spoiler_and_stuff_Choices;
	if Spoiler_and_stuff_Choice is:
		-- "Spoil me Dovah daddy!":
			say "     [bold type]YOUR WISH IS GRANTED![roman type]";
			LineBreak;
			say "     [italic type]Protective cult[roman type]: Embark on quests with Arlene's crewmates to rescue humans from bondage throughout the city's various slaver rings. Along the way you pick up a number of husky bitches for your cultists to train and play with. As a result, this path has the highest possible growth rate and features minor pet play, human X anthro, and milky yuri goodness. Further, rebelling against Tiamat is far easier as your brood and cultists will be more inclined to follow you should you ever choose to turn against the goddess. Unfortunately, this path will likely have a more kind-hearted tone that aspiring dragon overlords may find distasteful.";
			LineBreak;
			say "     [italic type]Hedonist cult[roman type]: Embrace your greedy inner predator while your priestess molds your followers into perfect broodmares, or delectable treats for yourself. The slowest growing cult by far as, for some reason, few people wish to become fodder for your growing splendor, though, with the right convincing, eager morsels can still be procured to sate your draconic urges. Beware though, as though the willing consumption and absorption of your followers will undoubtedly strengthen you, overindulgence may take its toll on your Dragon Breeder body. Yet such trifling concerns are nothing compared to the ravenous power and fertile glory that awaits committed preds and selfish gluttons who fully surrender to their draconic urges. Rebelling though will be rather difficult, if not impossible as precious few among your flock or flight will be willing, or even able to assist you should choose to walk this path. Fetishes include: body worship, absorption, weight gain among your followers, hyper pregnancy, Alt preg, optional multi boob, optional player weight gain, lactation, willing vore and willing UB with the PC as the pred. Note: this path is only open to preds with a tail maw.";
			WaitLinebreak;
			say "     [italic type]Ascension cult[roman type]: Spread the love to your adoring flock by assisting them in shedding their pitiable humanity so they may join your flight and further your ambitions, whatever they may be. This path is a firm middle ground in terms of growth as word of your gifts will surely attract fresh blood to the cult's ranks for few can resist the lure of power and immortality only you can offer. Rebellion is markedly easier compared to the hedonism path, yet some among your flock and spawn will still need some convincing to join you in open revolt against the goddess. Fetishes include: Gradually TFs, Taur X Taur, Taur X anthro, optional UB with the PC as pred, and the most depraved fetish of all... handholding.";
			say "[dovhadaddyout]";
		-- "No thanks.":
			say "     [bold type]Very well.[roman type]";
			say "[dovhadaddyout]";

to say dovhadaddyout:
	say "     How do you wish to run your cult?";
	LineBreak;
	let cultist_creed_Choices be a list of text;
	add "Protective cult dedicated to saving and preserving human life." to cultist_creed_Choices; 
	if Intelligence of Galaxite is 2:
		add "Pleasure cult made to service your needs and swell your brood." to cultist_creed_Choices;
	add "Transformative cult driven to uplift humanity from its grotesque condition." to cultist_creed_Choices;
	let cultist_creed_Choice be what the player chooses from cultist_creed_Choices;
	if cultist_creed_Choice is:
		-- "Protective cult dedicated to saving and preserving human life.":
			say "     Spreading your wings outward, you flare your chromatophores in a brilliant mix of hopeful platinum and faithful gold as you inform your modest flock of faithful humans of your intent to shelter and protect this world from harm. Too long have your former kin huddled in fear of the aberrant mutants and nameless horrors prowling the lands. Too long have they been shackled to the words of false prophets that offer not but empty words, and promises of salvation in the hereafter. Too long have they wallowed in ignorance of the goddess's power, love, and the many, you pause to languidly flexing powerful tauric body before your faithful, much to their delight as their eyes wander your chiseled core and opalescent hide. Gifts she would happily bestow upon them in the here and now, if only they would open their hearts and legs to her, and chosen angels, you simper, as you watch several of your follower eyes widen with unvarnished rapture. Together, they will save not only themselves, but all of humanity from being consumed by the nanites and foul creatures that dare to blight this world and seek to twist its people to their will. For unlike the imaginary deus of this sphere, the goddess accepts humanity for who they are and wishes no harm to come to this world, or its people.";
			say "     Yet salvation will not come easily as, though her eyes have turned upon this world, in order for her to manifest and bring order to chaos she will require their aid in bolstering your flight's numbers. But dread not, you beam, they will not be alone in this task as your flight shall endeavor to save as many of their ilk as possible, so together they can usher in an age of human supremacy under the protective talon of dragon kind. In the meantime, they should rejoice, for soon your flight shall take to the city to bring the goddess's wrath upon the mutant, the heretic, and the alien! Ol fala han klovve eth! You bellow, roughly slamming your tail upon the ground. 'Ol fala han klovve eth!' Your flock intones with a brassy fervor. Very good, you rumble affectionately, then inform them they are dismissed and free to return to their duties with your blessing. In the meantime, you will confer with your priestess so you begin the search for more souls in need of salvation. 'Yes mistress!' your followers cheer as they scurry to their feet and bolt in every direction.";
			WaitLineBreak;
			say "     As they flutter off into the various passage ways dotting the hall, the captain, er, Arlene you mentally correct yourself saunters up beside you with a cocksure grin on hir muzzle, saying, 'Yar quite dat lofty wee speech dare my dragon, or shoulds I'z be saying Vaysun da Kai Monah,' through a low chuckle as shi hooks hir arm about yours and playfully nuzzles hir coarse snoot against your silky perpetually-lubed core. 'Why,' shi whispers, 'I'z almost believe ya cared fir dis scurvy lot of willowy pig skins, still hope be a most tender balm, one we'z likely be needing un good supply to get this place ship shape any time soon. Now,' shi continues gesturing to a modest rent in the eastern section of this main hall with hir tail while lightly tugging on your arm as if beckoning you to follow. 'As fortune would have it, my lovely, me and mine might have a lead or two on some right nasty boyos what been capturing more than their fair share of pig skins dat ya might be interested in.'";
			say "     Duly curious, you allow Arlene to lead on as shi guides you into a spacious, passably lit room with a number of battery-powered prop lights fashioned into the shape of waist-high wrought iron candelabras illuminating a smoothed cavern furnished with a modest red metal four-poster bed hosting a ritzy creamy velvet sheets alongside several throw pillows. Its floors meanwhile have a number of thick furry hides thrown down upon while simple blue and gold cloth banners bearing your scalie visage have been hung on the slate walls. Likely sensing your eyes wandering hir abode, shi gently disentangles hirself from you and struts to the center of the room rumbling, 'Admiring me wee hidey-hole me dragon, tis nothing grand but pig skins respect these little displays, but back to the business at hand,' as shi seats hirself upon hir serviceable bed. 'Yar see,' shi says, playfully fanning hir before you, 'not too long before we'z met. Da crew un I caught wind of group [']O dem dogger boyos and puppy lasses rounding up the pig skins for sale upon the burgeoning flesh trade growing in dis [']ere city. Now while this place taint no Tortuga, dare still be a might lick of coin in peddling pure lasses to the masses,' shi hums, with a covetous glint flashes across hir selachian eyes.";
			WaitLineBreak;
			say "     Why's that, you rumble. 'Because me heart, it be easier to turn them into whatever manner [']O beastie yar soul could imagine. Sometime doe, ya find a rare un what's resistant to da change and fir whatever reason, lots [']O does pig skins seem to be able ta whelp a pureblooded copy of whatever boyo puts a bun in their bonnets,' Arlene cackles, hir paws briefly gliding along the graceful gray curves of hir tone midriff as shi traces the supple borders of two-toned hide. 'Why me crew un I once thought [']bout paying dem doggos a visit to see what manner of plunder they'd managed to acquire. But fir all their softness, there were a lot [']O of gitz in dat pack, so we let them be. Still,' shi adds with a predatory click of hir teeth, 'that was then me heart, now I'z got your sea devils and her most worshipfulness blessing it should be right milk run to shanghai use some fresh blood. I'z just need a wee while to send the little un's to see if dem bilge rats are still about. Course, if in your looking to pass a neck [']O time,' shi purrs with lustful trill, reclining ever-so-slightly onto hir bed while arching hir back at an inviting angle, 'the crew could always use new members to fill out our ranks...'";
			LineBreak;
			say "     [bold type] Author's note: cult content ends here for in the meantime feel free to play with your toy and build your numbers. If you're a backer though, please cast your vote on our patreon page to help decide which path gets developed next.[roman type]";
			now under sea is resolved;
			move player to Priestess's Chamber;
			now loyalty of Dragon Cultist is 1;
			increase XP of player by 50;
			increase score by 25;
			now HP of Arlene is 1;
		-- "Pleasure cult made to service your needs and swell your brood.":
			say "     Rumbling happily at the sight of the delectable treats arrayed before you, you prowl up to them, strobing your chromatophores a lurid pink. You commandingly cup your foretalon about the chin of your lowly followers, and inform them in an imposing, yet loving draconic trill of their glorious purpose as your favored harem and caretakers of your young. For only through their service to the goddess's draconic angels will this world be spared from the horror stalking it, but fear not, you rumble tracing your claws about the lush maiden's eve's orange. There is both bliss and glory to be found in submission as they will have the privilege of carrying the seeds of this world's rebirth into a paradise of coldblooded perfection under the goddess's benevolent thumb. No longer will they need suffer under this insipid leadership of short-sighted apes, or endure the depravations of false gods that would offer nothing but empty words and the hollow promise of rewards in the hereafter.";
			say "     Under you, you trill in abject delight as a preyish quiver passes through the puny warmblood as your words coil about her like tempting serpents on a vine. They will experience the boundless elysium of brood motherdom and revel in the heavenly changes your clutches will imbue upon them. In time, their broods and names could echo through the numberless spheres as their angelic young work to bring order and stability to the chaos of the eternal ocean. As their fame as broodmares grows, so too shall their esteem in the eyes of the goddess for her rewards are palpable things of the here and now. Tiamat rewards service with life everlasting and power equal to the mightiest wyrm to those with courage to bring will to power. In time, they may even earn ascension to the rank of priestess and gain greater gifts, or be granted worlds of their own to rule in the goddess's name.";
			WaitLineBreak;
			say "     And of course, you chirp invitingly as your proudly flaunt your [one of]alluring[or]athletic[or]predatory[or]powerful[or]curvaceous[or]tauric[or]dominant[or]reptilian[or]draconic[or]regal[at random] form before them, the transcendental rapture of servicing and, you pause to run your bifracted tongue along your fangs. Nourishing your majesty awaits them, for as great and terrible as you may be, you simper flexing your impressive wings before them as you bath the area in an enthralling ballet of pink and silver light. Your current form is but a fraction of what is required for the salvation of this sphere, and only through their devotion to you and the goddess's will shall you become strong enough to herald in her coming. Some among them may even earn the right to become a part of your nascent divinity, or perhaps even adopted into the ranks of your flight should they manage to distinguish themselves.";
			say "     This said, you tease, releasing your hold on the little human's chin, much work needs to be done before the goddess can be summoned into this world and deliver it from the creeping doom the unworthy leadership of this place have brought upon. To that end, you expect your delicious thralls to service your flight without question and blanket this city in cold-blooded perfection! Ol fala han klovve eth! You roar with a mighty thump of your tail upon the cavern floor. 'Ol fala han klovve eth!' the eager morsels bellow as they switch to a kneeling position, cup their hand to their breast then flash the same two-head dragon symbol your brood displayed to you. Rumbling in a pleased draconic cadence, you dismiss the puny manlets with a commanding flick of your tail telling them to return to their duties with your blessing, and watch as they quickly scurry away in every direction.";
			WaitLineBreak;
			say "     As they vanish into the gloomier sections of your hallowed temple, the captain, er, Arlene, you internally correct yourself, struts up to you with a vivacious grin on hir snoot, saying, 'Yar, now be da way ta light a fire in da pig skins['] muffs, me dragon, or should I'z be say'in, Vaysun da Kai Monah?' as shi jovially claps hir webbed mitts in approval. Shrugging, you tell hir you have no great preference as the title much like this cult is merely a tool to herald in the goddess and reap your just reward. '*Ha-ha* I loves it when ya talk like dat me heart, I'z knewz I had a right good feeling about ye. Now come along I'd like ta have a few wee words with ye in private before we'z get down to business all proper like,' Arlene chuckles, motioning for you to follow hir with a casually flick of hir finned tail towards a hole in eastern section of the hall. Rumbling in neutral tone, you gesture for hir to proceed and fall in step with the sultry corsair as shi leads you through the modest rent in the earth.";
			say "     Emerging on the other side, your abyssal gaze is greeted by the sight of a spacious, passably lit room with a number of battery-powered prop lights fashioned into the shape of waist-high wrought iron candelabras illuminating a smoothed cavern furnished with a modest red metal four-poster bed hosting a ritzy creamy velvet sheets alongside several throw pillows. Its floors meanwhile have a number of thick furry hides thrown down upon while simple blue and gold cloth banners bearing your scalie visage have been hung on the slate walls. Chuffing, you offhandedly compliment the bawdy herm on what shi's down with the place. 'Daw it nutting special just some old fur me an dem sea beasties found while we was cleaning out me old lair, but still,' shi crows as shi leisurely strides towards hir bed and proudly seats hirself upon while casually fanning paws before you. 'It serves its purpose and reminds the pig skins [']O da way of things. Un ye be happy to hear that our wee sea devils and dem big fishy boyos are already hard at work find us more plunder. [']N speaking [']O which, my and me mates put your share in the Treasury as da lasses have come to call it.'";
			WaitLineBreak;
			say "     'Course,' shi hums with covetous glint in her selachian eyes, 'we be needing more bodies on da books if in we want to really pull in the riches [']O da neath. Not ta mention, our wee piggies are going to need some more help ta get this place ship shape any time soon.' Naturally, you rumble, feeling your lips curl into a draconic smirk at the thought of your servants alongside your beatific brood have dredged from the depths, and what future wonders await you. 'Yar-har-har, I know that look well me lovely, un I couldn't be agreeing more! This [']ear deal [']O yours with her worshipfulness be fine one indeed! Never before have I'z dreamed of commanding sea beastie like them big boyos out in the depths. Un,' Arlene rumbles in deep brassy trills as shi playfully paws at hir tight creamy midriff, 'if in ya have the time perhaps ya wouldn't mind leave me with fresh shiver in me timbers...'";
			now under sea is resolved;
			move player to Priestess's Chamber;
			now loyalty of Dragon Cultist is 2;
			increase XP of player by 50;
			increase score by 25;
			now HP of Arlene is 1;
		-- "Transformative cult driven to uplift humanity from its grotesque condition.":
			say "     Gleefully admiring the [']fresh clay['] arrayed before you, you theatrically flare your wings and bathe the area in a soft ballet of mercurial silver light as you proudly declare you have come to free your faithful from the shackles of the human form and raise them to the lofty realm of draconic perfection. For humanity's time is nearing its end, and by embracing the path of ascension will they be able to not only survive, but thrive in this new new world. As unlike the weak surface level and ofttimes fleeting transformation the insipid ferals have tried to force upon them, you offer them a chance to truly become a mighty wyrms of legend. You rumble, proudly tracing a claw along the rich scales decorating your imperial core, much to the delight of your followers as their eyes lovingly glide along the sleek curves of your tauric form. Untouchable by time and entropy, their eternal bodies shall never know the weakness of old age, nor the limits of the mortal form. They shall wield powers dreamt of only in storybooks and the boundless joy of flight, should they prove worthy, they may even be granted powers equal to the false gods of this sphere.";
			say "     Never again will they know fear or doubt, for the mutant, heretic, and alien that dare trespass upon this sphere shall quake at their great and terrible passage! All you, and the goddess, ask in return is that they accept her place as the one true deus, and aid you in growing your flight so that your combined faith in Tiamat may at last call her to this world. Then she can put an end to the chaos ravaging these lands and usher forth an age of coldblooded perfection and flawless order! You roar, briefly rearing up onto your hindlegs and buffeting the crowd with a mighty flap of your wings, eliciting a low chorus of ooh's and aah's from the little humans as they shamelessly admire your imperial majesty. More than this, those who distinguish themselves may one day earn the right to conquer worlds of their own and spread their flight's names and dominion to the many corners of the eternal ocean in the goddess's name. But to do this, they must show their devotion to you, and your spawn as heavenly beings and embrace their holy roles as dragon mothers as well as heed the words of your priestess.";
			WaitLineBreak;
			say "     For only then, when they have fully given themselves to the cause will they earn the right to stand amongst the goddess's chosen angels and birth the salvation this world craves! Ol fala han klovve eth! 'Ol fala han klovve eth!' the little humans cry as many among their number lustfully paw at their toned tums in anticipation. Well spoken little mouses, you crow, now go attend to their future flights needs and revel in the changes that are to come! You commandingly thump your tail against the ground to dismiss your followers. In unison, the dragons-to-be move into a kneeling position and cup their hands to their breast and flash you the same two-headed dragon symbol your progeny displayed to you not all that long ago before hurriedly scattering about the temple with a joyous spring in their step. Watching them go, the captain, er, Arlene you mentally correct yourself saunters up to you with confused, yet oddly pleased look on hir muzzle. 'Quite the promise there me dragon or Vaysun da Kai Monah?' Shi chirps, idly flick hir tail behind hirself. 'I never took ye for the power sharing sort, but I'z suppose the pig skins will appreciate what yar doing for dem. Assuming this doesn't all go to their heads,' shi chuckles.";
			say "     Shrugging, you tell hir not to worry, besides, Tiamat requires a great many supplicants. What better draw is there then the promise of draconic ascension and the chance to wield her power? 'Da ya got me there me dragon, doe I'z hope ye can make good on yer word, fir I'z seen what yer kind can do when roused to anger.' Huffing, you brush aside such concerns with a wave of your scalie mitts and inform Arlene that is a problem for the future. Besides, the nanites dwelling within you and your spawn can be bent to service your needs in the interregnum. 'Ya-har, you might make a right good snake oil salesmen me lovely, now come along and let's discuss how to get this place shipshape,' shi chuckles mirthfully as shi gestures to a large hole nestled along the eastern wall with hir finned tail. Nodding, you fall in beside hir and stride forward together though the opening.";
			WaitLineBreak;
			say "     Slipping through the narrow, by your standards, threshold, your abyssal eyes are greeted by the sight of of a spacious, passably lit room with a number of battery-powered prop lights fashioned into the shape of waist-high wrought iron candelabras illuminating a smoothed cavern furnished with a modest red metal four-poster bed hosting a ritzy creamy velvet sheets alongside several throw pillows. Its floors meanwhile have a number of thick furry hides thrown down upon while simple blue and gold cloth banners bearing your scalie visage have been hung on the slate walls. Likely noting the molten glow of your many eyes waltzing about the area, Arlene coyly steps before with a mischievous gleam in hir eyes and says, 'Admiring my home away from home, me heart?' You nod, though you're not sure you'd use the term admire. 'Da tis simple set furnished with wee bits un bobs taken from me old lair, yet it serves its purpose well enough to remind the pig skins of their place. Still, der be much more to be desired if we're ever going to make this damp hole in the wall a temple worthy enough of her worshipfulness.' Arlene titters as shi seats hirself upon hir bed and playfully fans hir tail beside hirself.";
			say "     Rumbling in agreement, the great work is going to need more than its fair share of fresh blood and material if they are to comply with the goddess command to bejewel these halls in her name. 'Right ya are, me wonderous wyrm, thankfully fir us both dem boyos have been helping me un me mates plunder what we can from the loot stored in Pirate Island. Un our lovely sea devils have quite the boon too!' shi hums, leaning back onto hir bed and longingly gazes at the tight toned curves of hir hale creamy midriff. 'With them at our back, the girls un I have been able to suss out no small amount of plunder lurking in the city. Course,' Arlene purrs, idly tracing hir tail along the lush borders of hir two-toned tum, 'could always use a few more bodies to,' shi pauses as lips curl into a voracious grin, 'fill out the ranks...'";
			now under sea is resolved;
			move player to Priestess's Chamber;
			now loyalty of Dragon Cultist is 3;
			increase XP of player by 50;
			increase score by 25;
			now HP of Arlene is 1;


Arlene ends here.